  "text": "3) UAV-Based IoT Platforms: Providing real-time data is a significant function of unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs), which could make images or videos of damaged nuclear reactors or other disasters. UAVs can be connected to all kinds of IoT sensors and can be used to form a comprehensive P2P platform in the air [CITATION_1] .",
